reviewText: When chosing top latino videos for 2002, I think some other ones could have been put in. I like to think I know what's going on with latino music, but I had never heard of some of these artists! Videos worth watching over and over again are: alejandro sanz, la oreja de van gogh and shalim. Maybe a few more... I think there are better video compiliations for that year out there!

01.  La Bomba (Caribbean Funk Mix) - Azul Azul
02.  Slo quiero amarte - Ricky Martin
03.  Slo tus canciones - Daniela Herrero
04.  Con cada beso (balada) - Huey Dunbar
05.  Cudate - La Oreja de Van Gogh

07.  Muy dentro de m (You Sang to Me) - Marc Anthony
08.  Love Colada - OV7
09.  Pensando en t - Mara Bestar
10.  Seorita a m me gusta su style - Los Rabanes

13.  Celia's Oye como va - Celia Cruz
14.  El Carpintero del amor - Andres Cepeda
